  <text>
    <body>
  <div type="scene" n="3">
    <head>SCENE III.</head>
    <stage type='personnages'><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">HERMIONNE, CLEONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">HERMIONE, CLEONE. </rdg>
      </app></stage>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">HERMIONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">HERMIONE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="837">
ATtendois-tu, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Cleonne, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">Cleone, </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E #F">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">vn </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">courroux </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">couroux </rdg>
      </app>
si modeste&#160;? </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">CLEONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">CLEONE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="838">
La douleur qui se 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">taist </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">taît </rdg>
      </app>
n'en est que plus funeste. </l>

<l n="839">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E #F">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">Ie </rdg>
      </app>
le plains. D'autant plus 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">qu'Auteur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">qu'auteur </rdg>
      </app>
de son 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">ennuy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">ennui, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="840">
Le coup qui l'a perdu n'est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">party </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">parti </rdg>
      </app>
que de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">luy. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">lui. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="841">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Contez, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Contez </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Comptés </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#E">Comptez </rdg>
      </app>
depuis quel 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #F">tẽps </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D #E">temps </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">vostre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">vôtre </rdg>
      </app>
hymen se 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">prépare. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">prepare. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="842">
Il a parlé, Madame, &amp; Pyrrhus se 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">déclare. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">declare. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">HERMIONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">HERMIONE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="843">
Tu crois que Pyrrhus craint&#160;? Et que craint-il encor&#160;? </l>

<l n="844">
Des Peuples, qui dix ans ont 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">fuy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">fui </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E #F">devant </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">deuant </rdg>
      </app>
Hector&#160;? </l>

<l n="845">
Qui cent fois 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">effrayez </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">effraiés </rdg>
      </app>
de l'absence 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E #F">d'Achille, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">d'Achile, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="846">
Dans leurs vaisseaux 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">brulans </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">brûlans </rdg>
      </app>
ont cherché leur azile, </l>

<l n="847">
Et qu'on verroit encor, sans 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">l'appuy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">l'appui </rdg>
      </app>
de son Fils, </l>

<l n="848">
Redemander Helene aux Troyens 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">impunis&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">impunis. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="849">
Non, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Cleonne, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">Cleone, </rdg>
      </app>
il n'est point 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Ennemy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">Ennemi </rdg>
      </app>
de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">luy-mesme, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">lui-mesme, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">lui-même, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#E">luy-même, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="850">
Il veut tout ce qu'il fait, &amp; s'il 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #F">m'espouse, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D #E">m'épouse, </rdg>
      </app>
il m'aime. </l>

<l n="851">
Mais qu'Oreste à son gré m'impute ses douleurs. </l>

<l n="852">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #E #F">N'avons-nous </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">N'auons-nous </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">N'avons&#160;nous </rdg>
      </app>
d'entretien que 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E #F">celuy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">celui </rdg>
      </app>
de ses pleurs&#160;? </l>

<l n="853">
Pyrrhus 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E #F">revient </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">reuient </rdg>
      </app>
à nous. Hé bien, chere 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Cleonne, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Cleone, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">Cleone. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="854">
Conçois-tu les transports de l'heureuse 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #F">Hermionne&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Hermiõne&#160;? </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">Hermione&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="855">
Sçais-tu quel est Pyrrhus&#160;? 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">T'és-tu </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">T'es-tu </rdg>
      </app>
fait raconter </l>

<l n="856">
Le nombre des 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">Exploits... </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">Exploits.. </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#E">exploits.. </rdg>
      </app>
Mais qui les peut 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">conter&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">compter&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="857">
Intrepide, &amp; par tout 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#F">suivy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">suiuy </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">suivi </rdg>
      </app>
de la 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #F">Victoire, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D #E">victoire, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="858">
Charmant, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">Fidelle </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">fidelle, </rdg>
      </app>
enfin, rien 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">de </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">ne </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E #F">manque </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">mãque </rdg>
      </app>
à sa 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">Gloire. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">gloire. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="859.1">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #D #F">Songe.... </lem>
        <rdg wit="#E">Songe... </rdg>
      </app>
</l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">CLEONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">CLEONE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="859.2">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">Dissimulez. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">Dissimulés. </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">Vostre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">Vôtre </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E #F">Rivale </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">Riuale </rdg>
      </app>
en pleurs, </l>
<l n="860">
Vient à vos 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E #F">pieds </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">piez </rdg>
      </app>
sans doute apporter ses douleurs. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #F">HERMIONNE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D #E">HERMIONE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="861">
Dieux&#160;! Ne puis-je à ma 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E #F">joye </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">joie </rdg>
      </app>
abandonner mon ame&#160;? </l>

<l n="862.1">
Sortons. Que 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E #F">luy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">lui </rdg>
      </app>
dirois-je&#160;? </l>
</sp>
</div>
